manifests.contents:
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "signup-sequencer"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[[bench]]
path = "criterion.rs"
name = "criterion"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = false
required-features = ["bench", "proptest"]

[[test]]
path = "tests/integration-tests.rs"
name = "integration-tests"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "signup-sequencer"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
build = "build.rs"
authors = ["Remco Bloemen <remco@worldcoin.org>", "Lucas Ege <lucas@worldcoin.org>"]
description = "A tool that processes WorldID signups on-chain."
homepage = "https://github.com/worldcoin/signup-sequencer"
readme = "Readme.md"
keywords = ["worldcoin", "protocol", "signup"]
categories = ["cryptography::cryptocurrencies"]
license-file = "mit-license.md"
repository = "https://github.com/worldcoin/signup-sequencer"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
async-stream = "0.3.3"
async-trait = "0.1.64"
axum = "0.6.4"
axum-server = "0.4.4"
chrono = "0.4.19"
eyre = "0.6"
futures = "0.3"
once_cell = "1.8"
prometheus = "0.13.3"
serde_json = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-futures = "0.2"
url = "2.2"

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1.0.68"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.cli-batteries]
version = "0.4.0"
features = ["signals", "prometheus", "metered-allocator", "otlp"]

[dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.4"
features = ["async_tokio"]
optional = true

[dependencies.ethers]
version = "1.0.0"
features = ["ws", "ipc", "openssl", "abigen"]

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "^0.3"

[dependencies.hyper]
version = "^0.14.17"
features = ["server", "tcp", "http1", "http2"]

[dependencies.proptest]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.14"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.ruint]
version = "1.3"
features = ["primitive-types", "sqlx"]

[dependencies.semaphore]
git = "https://github.com/worldcoin/semaphore-rs"
branch = "main"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "any", "sqlite", "postgres"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.17"
features = ["signal", "macros", "rt", "sync", "time", "rt-multi-thread", "tracing"]

[dev-dependencies]
hex = "0.4.3"
hex-literal = "0.3"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3.11"
tracing-test = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies.cli-batteries]
version = "0.4.0"
features = ["mock-shutdown"]

[dev-dependencies.proptest]
version = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies.serial_test]
version = "1.0.0"

[build-dependencies]
cli-batteries = "0.4.0"

[features]
bench = ["criterion", "proptest"]
default = []
mimalloc = ["cli-batteries/mimalloc"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "signup_sequencer"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
[profile.release]
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
overflow-checks = true

[profile.release.package]

[profile.dev]
panic = "abort"
[profile.dev.package."*"]
opt-level = 3
